as]]'' || Agent Rance || Episode: \"There's Only One Sidney Bristow\"\n|-\n || ''[[Smith (TV series)|Smith]]'' || Mr. Corey || Episode: \"Three\"\n|-\n || ''[[Without a Trace]]'' || Thomas Biggs || Episode: \"Watch Over Me\"\n|-\n| 2006\u201307 || ''[[Supernatural (U.S. TV series)|Supernatural]]'' || Gordon Walker || 4 episodes\n|-\n|rowspan=2| 2007 || ''[[Shark (U.S. TV series)|Shark]]'' || Quenton North || Episode: \"Teacher's Pet\"\n|-\n || ''[[Standoff (TV series)|Standoff]]'' || Russell Marsh || Episode: \"Lie to Me\"\n|-\n| 2007\u201313 || ''[[Army Wives]]'' || Roland Burton || 107 episodes\n|-\n| 2008 || ''[[Eli Stone]]'' || David Mosley || Episode: \"Patience\"\n|-\n| 2010 || ''[[Medium (TV series)|Medium]]'' || Todd Gillis || Episode: \"The People in Your Neighborhood\"\n|-\n|rowspan=3| 2011 || ''[[Detroit 1-8-7]]'' || Cameron Jones || Episode: \"Ice Man/Malibu\"\n|-\n || ''[[The Good Wife]]'' || Andrew Boylan || Episode: \"Feeding the Rat\"\n|-\n|| ''[[Harry's Law]]'' || Mr. Thomas || Episode: \"American Girl\"\n|-\n| 2012 || ''[[Nikita (TV series)|Nikita]]'' || Nick Anson || Episode: \"True Believer\"\n|-\n| 2012\u201313 || ''[[Person of Interest (TV series)|Person of Interest]]'' || Detective Cal Beecher || 6 episodes\n|-\n| 2013 || ''[[NCIS (TV series)|NCIS]]'' || Elijah Banner || Episode: \"Devil's Triad\"\n|-\n|rowspan=2| 2014 || ''[[The Mentalist]]'' || Agent Higgins || Episode: \"White Lines\"\n|-\n|| ''[[Masters of Sex]]'' || Marcus || Episode: \"Story of My Life\"\n|-\n|rowspan=2| 2015 || ''[[Castle (TV series)|Castle]]'' || Ed Redley || Episode: \"The Wrong Stuff\"\n|-\n || ''[[Criminal Minds]]'' || Fitz || Episode: \"Beyond Borders\"\n|-\n| 2016 || ''[[The People v. O. J. Simpson: American Crime Story|The People v. O. J. Simpson:<br>American Crime Story]]'' ||[[Christopher Darden]]|| 10 episodes\n|-\n| 2016\u2013present || ''[[This Is Us (TV series)|This Is Us]]'' || Randall Pearson || Main role \n|-\n|rowspan=2| 2017 || ''[[Insecure (TV series)|Insecure]]'' || Lionel || 2 episodes\n|-\n|| ''[[Running Wild with Bear Grylls]]'' ||  Himself || Episode: \"Sterling K. Brown\"\n|-\n|rowspan=4|2018 || ''[[Saturday Night Live]]'' || Himself (host) || Episode: \"Sterling K. Brown/[[James Bay (singer)|James Bay]]\"\n|- \n|| ''[[Brooklyn Nine-Nine]]'' || Philip Davidson || Episode: \"The Box\"\n|- \n|| ''Black Love'' || Himself || 2 episodes\n|-\n| ''[[Robot Chicken]]'' || Various voices || Episode: \"Shall I Visit the Dinosaurs?\"\n|-\n|rowspan=3|2019 || ''[[The Unauthorized Bash Brothers Experience]]'' || [[Sia (musician)|Sia]] || TV special\n|-\n||''[[Sesame Street]]'' || Himself || Episode: \"Sesame Street 50th Anniversary\"\n|-\n||''[[The Marvelous Mrs. Maisel]]'' || Reggie || 4 episodes\n|-\n| 2019\u201320 || ''[[One Day at Disney (film)|One Day at Disney]]'' || Narrator || 52 episodes\n|-\n| 2020 || ''[[Kipo and the Age of Wonderbeasts]]'' || Lio Oak (voice) || Main role\n|}\n\n===Music videos===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|-\n! Year !! Artist !! Title !! Role\n|-\n| 2019 ||[[The Lonely Island]] (feat. [[Sia (musician)|Sia]]) || \"Oakland Nights\" || Sia\n|}\n\n===Stage===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|-\n! Year !! Theater !! Show !! Role\n|-\n| rowspan=2 | 2002\n| [[Public Theater]] [[Delacorte Theater]]\n| ''[[Twelfth Night]]''\n| Antonio\n|-\n| National Actor's Theatre\n| ''The Resistible Rise of Arturo Ui''\n| Goodwill\n|-\n| 2006\n| [[Public Theater]] [[Delacorte Theater]]\n| ''[[Macbeth]]''\n| [[Macduff (Macbeth)|Macduff]]\n|-\n| rowspan=2 | 2009\n| rowspan=4 | [[Public Theater]] [[Anspacher Theater]]\n| ''[[The Brother/Sister Plays]] Part 1: In The Red and Brown Water''\n| Shango\n|-\n| ''The Brother/Sister Plays Part 2: The Brothers Size and Marcus; or the Secret of Sweet''\n| Shua\n|-\n| rowspan=2 | 2014\n| rowspan=2 | ''Father Comes Home From the Wars (Parts 1, 2, & 3)''\n| Hero/Ulysses\n|-\n| Hero\n|}\n\n==Awards and nominations==\n{{Main|List of awards and nominations received by Sterl